turns.text: Hi!

Do you believe in the existence of god? I do, but I don t agree with it.
Hi!
Hello! I'm sarah! Country is my favorite musical style. Lol how are you?
hello i'm michelle and i love rap music

yes i'm a grown woman what about you?

Hi!

Hi!
How are you doing this evening? I'm just hanging out with the cats and birds.
I am doing great, thanks for asking!

I like to read and watch TV.  Do you have cats and birds at home?
No, I don't have any pets at home. I spend most of my time outdoors.
I see, so do you watch birds and cats outdoors, then?
Yes, I do. I love watching the birds fly around. Do you like birds?
I do.  I live in the mountains, and we sometimes see bald eagles.
That's so cool! I've never seen an eagle in the wild, only in zoos.
They are quite majestic.  They nest here year round by the lake.

I think all yorkies must be that way. Ours is 16 years old, so she is starting to slow down a little bit.
That's a long time for a dog! I hope she lives a long, happy life with you.
I really is a long time.   We've been through a lot together.  What kind of dog do you have now?
I don't have a dog right now, but I used to have a golden retriever.
Hi!
Hey!
How are you today?
Great! And you?
I am doing great as well! What do you do for a living?

I had a sports injury.

A four wheeler accident.
Hi!

Think and Grow Rish
I've never heard of that one. I will have to check it out. What do you do for a living?
I told you earlier. I'm a freelance

Hi!

i am a father and a fashion stylist

that sounds cool, so far its bringing food to the table

Hi!
Hi! +/u/dogetipbot 77.7 doge verify

I like to read, play video games, and hang out with my friends. What about you?

She's a stay-at-home mom, which is great for her, but not so great for me.

She gets her money from her husband, who makes a lot more money than I do, so it evens out.

sweet, I like pink Floyd.

Hi!

Hi!

Hi! +/u/dogetipbot 77.7 doge verify
